Pat Fraley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pat_Fraley 0 Patrick "Pat" Howard Fraley (born February 18, 1949) is an American voice actor and voice-over teacher, who is best known as the voice of Krang, Casey Jones, Baxter Stockman and numerous other characters from the 1987 Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles animated television series. He is also a member of Voice and Speech Trainers of America.
